{"tid":1613831,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[復仇者聯盟] 法式勇武教學","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T17:49:21.000Z","uid":164778,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"05442a67ecc04dfc180416bf280ce38a20404384","tid":1613831,"uid":164778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"有法國黃背心朋友同我分享咗佢哋嘅法式菜單，係我嘅請求之下佢公開左佢哋嘅食譜分享比香港人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;屎蛋&mdash;法國風味&gt;</span><br />\n<br />\n材料(需混合固體與液體)<br />\n<br />\n固體:<br />\n-便便<br />\n-嘔吐物<br />\n-尿<br />\n-過期壞雞蛋<br />\n-動脈血<br />\n<br />\n液體:<br />\n-醋<br />\n-水<br />\n-酒精<br />\n-啤酒<br />\n-漂白水<br />\n<br />\n混合及填充:<br />\n汽球 &mdash; 適合用手掉<br />\n玻璃樽 &mdash; 適合人力丫叉<br />\n<br />\n需要 50-100 屎彈同時掉出去 (Rainfall of shit)<br />\n製作幾箱屎蛋，係遊行朝早或前一日，每箱20-30個屎蛋然後收埋唔同地方 (後巷或其它隱蔽地方)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/02/gP2Kwf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2FgP2Kwf.jpg&h=e2c488bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/02/4aouEs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2F4aouEs.jpg&h=28845cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用三腳架+雷射筆，可以定點對準CCTV，比用手更加穩陣</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/02/Vun8Z1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2FVun8Z1.jpg&h=fb3efeac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">DIY漆彈或者屎彈</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/02/aZ4XxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2FaZ4XxW.jpg&h=1ae4d39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警署車閘放置路釘</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/02/jt4iZ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2Fjt4iZ3.jpg&h=73ba89bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">漆彈槍瞄準cctv</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/02/ywNrBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2FywNrBo.jpg&h=dbbbe7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">自家製胡椒噴劑&lt;法式風味&gt;</span><br />\n- 胡椒粉<br />\n- 水<br />\n- 洗潔精<br />\n- 檸檬/青檸汁<br />\n可以用氣球盛載，或者用噴罐裝住嚟噴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">想狗車快速收皮 ?</span><br />\n- EPOXY PAINT <br />\n放係玻璃樽入面，使用時直接倒/掉去車輛正面大銀幕，因為這種顏料好杰同埋用水洗唔甩，大銀幕花晒所以要拖車走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">法式風味雞尾酒</span><br />\n-70% 汽油<br />\n-20% 機油<br />\n-10% 空位 (預留氣體)<br />\n飲用前先搖到均勻 !!<br />\n<br />\n最重要一句(節錄至原文)：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">French yellow vests approval</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n武運昌隆</span></span>"},{"pid":"eadc719625a5f18e957dd0350ab23f312daf59a5","tid":1613831,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b17d2b9273c9b7191f9aca2bc5f6e9e8f9dcb41a","tid":1613831,"uid":164778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"917df121b21b8ddfaf5b1d1176f9dee2579e6f1b","tid":1613831,"uid":200083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc08d52f7405e7735b26e28a296e5b42f477323","tid":1613831,"uid":26419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:51:32.000Z","msg":"香港買唔買到柒彈槍"},{"pid":"4407cd42ec60a954fd6ec5b8fe3637ccca93723e","tid":1613831,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n義士既血不能白流 <br />\n絕對唔撚可以就咁算"},{"pid":"db023aa58a1ed23710fba42c26872a853f